article.description: — Jose Placer scored 15 points as North Florida held off Kennesaw State 68-65 on Saturday.
article.headline: Placer carries North Florida over Kennesaw St. 68-65
article.linkText: Placer carries North Florida over Kennesaw St. 68-65
article.story: JACKSONVILLE, Fla. -- — Jose Placer scored 15 points as North Florida held off Kennesaw State 68-65 on Saturday. Carter Hendricksen scored 13 points for North Florida (6-10, 4-2 Atlantic Sun Conference), Emmanuel Adedoyin scored 10 and Jonathan Aybar grabbed eight rebounds. Spencer Rodgers had 21 points for the Owls (3-13, 0-8) who now have lost 11 straight. Chris Youngblood added 13 points and Jamie Lewis 10. The Ospreys also defeated Kennesaw State 69-54 on Friday. ------ For more AP college basketball coverage: https://apnews.com/Collegebasketball and http://twitter.com/AP--Top25 ------ This was generated by Automated Insights, http://www.automatedinsights.com/ap, using data from STATS LLC, https://www.stats.com
